    <div class="col-lg-7 mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-white"> As a growing business, do you want to scale fast and connect to your audience?</h1>
    <p class="text-white my-3">Our platform can help you achieve your objectives of scalability and constantly be in connection with your audience / customers. You can send bulk sms, trigger them over certain events, we are happy to help you achieve your specific use case and see you grow.</p>
