{{define "section"}}

<section id="services">
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col md-8 mx-auto text-center">
    <h6 class="text-primary"> Services </h6>
    <h1>Our Services </h1>
    <p>We offer a variety of services to help scale your business, since we understand how important it is to stay connected to customers.</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row g-4">
    {{template "card1"}}
    {{template "card2"}}
    {{template "card3"}}
    </div>
</div>
</section>
{{end}}

{{define "card1"}}
<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
    <div class="service card-effect">
    <div class="iconbox">
    <i class='bx bxs-chat'></i>
    </div>
    <h5 class="mt-4 mb-2">Bulk SMS</h5>
    <p>Send 1000+ SMS in a span of minutes, pay as you go, no need to constantly monitor and send SMS manually, we'll inform you if any messages fail to go through.</p>
    </div>
</div>
{{end}}

{{define "card2"}}
<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
    <div class="service card-effect">
    <div class="iconbox">
    <i class='bx bxs-chat'></i>
    </div>
    <h5 class="mt-4 mb-2">Software SMS integration </h5>
    <p>Do you have any Software that you would want to attach messaging functionality with? Would you want to send text messages to your audience / cutomers as their order is ready for pickup ? Or provide them with reciepts as SMS. If so we are happy to dicuss your use case, please get in touch.</p>
    </div>
</div>
{{end}}

{{define "card3"}}
<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
    <div class="service card-effect">
    <div class="iconbox">
    <i class='bx bxs-chat'></i>
    </div>
    <h5 class="mt-4 mb-2">SMS Terminal</h5>
    <p>Custom SMS terminal, to send SMS Whenever and Wherever. Send SMS to a single customer or Bulk SMS using a list of numbers in a spread sheet. Use our dashboard functionality to monitor messages delivered, in transit and that failed to send, all with your own custom phone number of choosing.</p>
    </div>
</div>
{{end}}

{{define "features"}}
